description:
Danny welcomes Tyler Duckworth back to the show to recap the state of pop culture, including the end of the Olympics, Celebrity Big Brother, and, of course, Housewives. Danny also welcomes Ms. Juicy, the Queen of Atlanta, the Queen of internet memes, and cast member of Lifetime's Little Women Atlanta. They chat about her show, her life, and lots more. The interview with Ms. Juicy starts at 47:12 :)

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
